---
layout: base.njk
title: "Health Calculator Tools"
description: "Free health calculators: BMI calculator, age calculator, and more. Results are for informational purposes only."
canonical: "https://everyday-tools.pages.dev/health/"
---

<div class="container">
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; Health Tools
  </nav>

  <h1>Health Calculator Tools</h1>
  <p class="category-intro">Free health metric calculators for personal use. All calculations run locally in your browser. Results are estimates for informational purposes only — consult a qualified healthcare professional for medical advice.</p>

  <div class="tool-list">
    {%- for tool in tools -%}
      {%- if tool.category == "health" -%}
        <div class="tool-card">
          <h2><a href="/health/{{ tool.slug }}/">{{ tool.name }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ tool.description }}</p>
          <a class="tool-link" href="/health/{{ tool.slug }}/">Open {{ tool.name }} &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>
